{"artefact":[["_response_info",{"status":"ok"}],["title","Motorcycle trainer fees"],["id","https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/motorcycle-trainer-fees.json"],["web_url","https://www.gov.uk/motorcycle-trainer-fees"],["format","answer"],["details",{"need_id":"B143","business_proposition":true,"alternative_title":"","overview":"Fees for becoming one of the different types a motorcycle trainer and registering with the Driving Standards Agency (DSA)","updated_at":"2012-10-07T09:36:56+00:00","body":"\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>There\u2019s no charge to take the compulsory basic training (<abbr title=\"Compulsory basic training\">CBT</abbr>) and direct access scheme (<abbr title=\"Direct access scheme\">DAS</abbr>) instructor assessments, but there are fees for other types of motorcycle trainer tests and registration.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2>Driving Standards Agency (<abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr>) special test fee</h2>\n\n<p>As a fully qualified motorcycle trainer you can take the <abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> special test if you want your skills tested to the highest standard.</p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Price</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><abbr title=\"Driving Standards Agency\">DSA</abbr> motorcycle special test</td>\n      <td>\u00a3163</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<h2>Register of post-test motorcycle trainers (<abbr title=\"Register of post-test motorcycle trainers\">RPMT</abbr>) fees</h2>\n\n<p>You have to pay a fee to take the qualifying tests and then register to join the <abbr title=\"Register of post-test motorcycle trainers\">RPMT</abbr> so you can give <a href=\"enhanced-rider-scheme/overview\" title=\"Enhanced rider scheme\">enhanced rider scheme</a> training. </p>\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Fee type</th>\n      <th>Price</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Starter pack</td>\n      <td>\u00a36.99</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Theory and hazard perception test</td>\n      <td>\u00a366</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Riding ability test</td>\n      <td>\u00a3114</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Instructional ability test</td>\n      <td>\u00a3114</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registration and renewal fee (1 year)</td>\n      <td>\u00a390</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td>Registration and renewal fee (4 years)</td>\n      <td>\u00a3240</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>You have to pay the full amount again if you don\u2019t pass any of the tests, and want to take another one.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There are different <a href=\"http://www.nidirect.gov.uk/index/information-and-services/motoring/driving-for-a-living/how-do-i-become-an-approved-motorcycle-instructor-ami.htm\" title=\"Fees for motorcycle trainers\" rel=\"external\">fees for motorcycle trainers</a> in Northern Ireland.</p>\n</div>\n\n"}],["tags",[{"title":"Teaching people to drive","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Becoming an instructor, applying for licences, booking tests and rules","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving%2Fteaching-people-to-drive","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving/teaching-people-to-drive"},"parent":{"title":"Driving","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/driving.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":"Book your driving test or get a tax disc online, find out the legal requirements for buying, owning, importing or scrapping a car or motorcycle, and read about your rights and responsibilities as a driver.","type":"section"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=driving","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/driving"},"parent":null}},{"title":"Business Link","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/tags/businesslink.json","web_url":null,"details":{"description":null,"type":"legacy_source"},"content_with_tag":{"id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/with_tag.json?tag=businesslink","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/browse/businesslink"},"parent":null}]],["related",[{"title":"Become a direct access scheme (DAS) motorcycle instructor","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/become-direct-access-scheme-motorcycle-instructor.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-direct-access-scheme-motorcycle-instructor","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"B890","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Become a DSA assessed CBT motorcycle instructor","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/become-dsa-assessed-cbt-motorcycle-instructor.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-dsa-assessed-cbt-motorcycle-instructor","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"B891","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Register of post-test motorcycle trainers (RPMT)","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/register-post-test-motorcycle-trainers-rpmt.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/register-post-test-motorcycle-trainers-rpmt","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"B911","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Set up and run a motorcycle approved training body (ATB)","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/set-up-run-motorcycle-approved-training-body-atb.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/set-up-run-motorcycle-approved-training-body-atb","format":"guide","details":{"need_id":"B982","business_proposition":true}},{"title":"Become a motorcycle instructor","id":"https://contentapi.production.alphagov.co.uk/become-a-motorcycle-instructor.json","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/become-a-motorcycle-instructor","format":"smart-answer","details":{"need_id":"2545","business_proposition":true}}]]],"parts":null}